#SFDC-Mass-Freeze-Users

Platform: Salesforce.com/Force.com, Apex code, Visualforce page, Custom Setting
Using native SFDC technology, provides a way to "freeze" all users in your org,
i.e. disabling them from logging in.
This is useful e.g. when you need to have the system offline for whatever reason.

##Features
* Mass freeze users
* Mass melt all frozen users
* Custom Setting to enable only specific users and profiles the ability to melt
* Custom Setting to control specific users and profiles that will not be frozen
* Will not freeze the current user :)
